ðŸ”¥ Scenario C: New version deployed â†’ service not loading

Check unit file:

vim /etc/systemd/system/myapp.service
systemctl daemon-reload
systemctl restart myapp

ðŸ”¥ Scenario D: Ports blocked after enabling firewall

Fix:

firewall-cmd --add-port=8080/tcp --permanent
firewall-cmd --reload
systemctl restart myapp

ðŸ”¥ Scenario E: Cron jobs not running

Check cron service:

